      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay good to know. i was getting a bit worried cuz i also feel kind of dizzy sometimes and my stomach feels weirdly heavy. i read online somewhere that you have to be careful with how much water you drink with lithium, but i feel like i'm drinking plenty. should i just try to drink even more water to help flush out any extra stuff that might be making me shaky?",
